          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "On 15 April, Minns said that he was considering the establishment of a permanent memorial to the victims of the attack",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
          "sentence": "An online condolence book was set up by the NSW government",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
          "sentence": "Queensland Premier Steven Miles offered full cooperation of his state's authorities in the investigation after it emerged that the perpetrator came from Queensland",
          "refs": [
